 "lrc": "[00:16.32]The screen lights up and I see your name\n[00:20.32]midnight turns into a little flame\n[00:24.40]I start typing, then I erase\n[00:28.48]like I’m standing right in front of your face\n[00:32.56]Is it still me that makes you smile\n[00:36.56]when my name shows up after a while?\n[00:39.20]Is it still me that makes you pause\n[00:44.72]before you answer just because?\n[00:48.80]Is it still me in your quiet room\n[00:50.88]when the night gets sweet and the lights go blue?\n[00:52.88]Is it still me that makes you sweat?\n[00:56.96]Is it still me you almost say\n[00:58.96]when you miss the hands that are far away?\n[01:05.12]Is it still me in your future plans\n[01:07.44]when you close your eyes and reach for my hands?\n[01:13.04]Still smiling when your name appears…\n[01:17.20]still pausing like you’re standing here…\n[01:20.72]still thinking of you when the lights go blue…\n[01:24.80]still feeling the heat from across the room…\n[01:30.40]You send questions like little sparks\n[01:32.48]landing soft in the dark\n[01:34.48]I read them once, then twice again\n[01:36.08]like every word knows where I’ve been\n[01:38.40]Yes, it’s still you that makes me smile\n[01:41.20]even from a thousand miles\n[01:45.52]Yes, it’s still you that makes me wait\n[01:49.28]just to feel my heartbeat change\n[01:53.60]Yes, it’s still you when the lights go low\n[01:56.08]and I miss the voice I already know\n[02:01.44]Yes, it’s still you that makes me sweat\n[02:05.76]Yes, it’s still you I want beside me\n[02:10.08]not just calling, not just typing\n[02:13.68]Yes, it’s still you in the life I see\n[02:16.80]but now I have some questions for me\n[02:22.14]Is it still me?\n[02:23.90]Is it still you?\n[02:25.90]In the late-night glow when the screen turns blue\n[02:30.06]Is it still us?\n[02:31.74]Do we still feel true?\n[02:34.22]With a whole wide world in between us two\n[02:38.46]Is it still me?\n[02:40.03]Is it still you?\n[02:42.22]When the bass rolls soft and the moon comes through\n[02:46.14]Send me your heart, I’ll send mine too\n[02:50.94]Is it still me?\n[02:52.38]Baby, it’s still you\n[02:58.94]Is it still me that makes you dream\n[03:01.26]when you’re tired of every little thing?\n[03:03.10]Is it still me you want to call\n[03:05.34]when your big plans start to feel too tall?\n[03:08.14]Is it still me you’re building for\n[03:10.70]when you save a little more and more?\n[03:15.26]Is it still me you want to hold\n[03:17.34]when New York nights get loud and cold?\n[03:19.42]Is it still me that slows your mind\n[03:21.74]when the whole world runs overtime?\n[03:24.38]Is it still me you’re coming home to\n[03:27.50]when the miles finally let us through?\n[03:31.90]Still dreaming when the world gets heavy…\n[03:35.90]still calling when my plans get messy…\n[03:39.42]still building, still saving, still choosing you…\n[03:43.66]still hearing your voice when the night turns blue…\n[03:48.38]Yes, it’s still you when I lose my way\n[03:50.38]you’re the calm in the noise of the day\n[03:52.06]Yes, it’s still you when I count what’s left\n[03:54.46]trying to become my very best\n[03:56.70]Yes, it’s still you when the city screams\n[03:58.46]still you in the center of all my dreams\n[04:00.78]Yes, it’s still you that I’m running to\n[04:02.62]every changed habit is a road to you\n[04:07.66]Then don’t just say it\n[04:09.66]I’ll prove it slow\n[04:11.66]Don’t just promise\n[04:13.74]Watch me grow\n[04:15.74]Don’t just miss me\n[04:17.66]I’ll make it real\n[04:19.34]Then tell me again\n[04:21.90]You know how I feel\n[04:24.14]Is it still me?\n[04:26.14]Is it still you?\n[04:28.06]In the late-night glow when the screen turns blue\n[04:32.06]Is it still us?\n[04:33.90]Do we still feel true?\n[04:36.06]With a whole wide world in between us two\n[04:39.18]Is it still me?\n[04:44.30]Is it still you?\n[04:44.38]When the bass rolls soft and the moon comes through\n[04:48.14]Send me your heart, I’ll send mine too\n[04:52.70]Is it still me?\n[04:55.42]Baby, it’s still you\n[04:57.98]Still me?\n[04:59.02]Still you.\n[04:59.98]Still us.\n"
